{"data":[{"date":"11:10 28/06","title":"Hitzlsperger: \"\u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/hitzlsperger-day-khong-phai-dt-duc-cua-chung-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u00fa s\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup 2018, c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Thomas Hitzlsperger l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ee9c \u00ea ch\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean t\u1edd Guardian, c\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c Hitzlsperger \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u00fd ch\u00ednh trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a anh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng l\u1ea1 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u00f2n thua trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai &ndash; nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i World Cup, \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c. M\u1ed9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111ang ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tr\u1ed1ng r\u1ed7ng khi vi\u1ebft nh\u1eefng d\u00f2ng n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, t\u00f4i mong ch\u1edd \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t m\u1eb7t t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, ch\u1edd m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y sinh l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i, \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c m\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra v\u1eady? Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 m\u00e3n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1. \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i k\u00e9m trong 2 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, v\u1edbi \u00c1o v\u00e0 Saudi Arabia. \u0110\u1ec3 suy ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hitzlsperger l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i\" title=\"Mario Gomez c\u0169ng chung n\u1ed7i bu\u1ed3n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i khi \u0110\u1ee9c thua H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/14.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Hitzlsperger l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ai lo l\u1eafng v\u00ec Joachim Low lu\u00f4n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh trong c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang t\u1ea1i Nga. Ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3i t\u1ed5 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n. Nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o, khi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169 \u0111ang b\u01b0\u1edbc sang giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tranh c\u00e3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c lo\u1ea1i Leroy Sane, sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf Man City. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh m\u1eabu m\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c c\u1ea7n trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, tr\u1ebb trung, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 nguy hi\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i &ndash; t\u00f4i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Muller. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i, v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c. Sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng, ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Joachim Low. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y n\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y k\u1ef3 l\u1ea1 \u1edf \u0110\u1ee9c, khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quen thu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y &ndash; \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng&rdquo; &ndash; Hitzlsperger l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/hummels-duc-da-choi-te-dan-deu-tu-nam-2017-469-189802.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/hummels-duc-da-choi-te-dan-deu-tu-nam-2017.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/hummels-duc-da-choi-te-dan-deu-tu-nam-2017-469-189802.html\">Hummels: \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 d\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2017</span><br>\r\nMats Hummels cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 d\u1ea7n t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2017.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-duc-vs-han-quoc-461-189779.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/13.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-duc-vs-han-quoc-461-189779.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nWorld Cup 2018 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i khi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 thua H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-2 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"675","checkdouble":"189821"},{"date":"09:32 28/06","title":"Gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp HLV Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 v\u1eabn c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/gianh-ve-di-tiep-hlv-thuy-sy-van-cam-thay-khong-hai-long.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Vladimir Petkovic n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 vs Costa Rica, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf \u0110\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 2-2 \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Costa Rica \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018, ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 s\u1ebd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111i ti\u1ebfp m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Brazil v\u00e0 Serbia.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Vladimir Petkovic n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 vs Costa Rica h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Vladimir Petkovic n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 vs Costa Rica h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/HLV-Vladimir-Petkovic-noi-ve-tran-Thuy-Sy-vs-Costa-Rica-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 h\u00f2a Costa Rica 2-2</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nV\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t cao, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf \u0110\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng d\u1ed3n l\u00ean ngay sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c. Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ee9c \u00e9p r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 2 l\u1ea7n v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nB\u00e0n thua tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd khi\u1ebfn Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 2-2. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-thuy-sy-vs-costa-rica-421-189789.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 vs Costa Rica</span> l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Vladimir Petkovic gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp b\u1edfi \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng gi\u1edd Brazil \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Serbia 2-0.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 sau 3 tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y s\u1ef9 c\u00f3 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m, h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E sau Brazil. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ea3ng E \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf \u0110\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Petkovic th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Vladimir Petkovic n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 vs Costa Rica, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf \u0110\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 2-2 \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Petkovic noi ve tran Thuy Sy vs Costa Rica\" title=\"HLV Petkovic n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 vs Costa Rica\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/gianh-ve-di-tiep-hlv-thuy-sy-van-cam-thay-khong-hai-long.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Petkovic n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 vs Costa Rica</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, tuy nhi\u00ean t\u00f4i kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 2 l\u1ea7n v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, song l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n&ldquo;Vi\u1ec7c Lichtsteiner v\u00e0 Schar b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, song Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 c\u00f3 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"674","checkdouble":"189823"},{"date":"09:44 28/06","title":"HLV Oscar Ramirez: \"Costa Rica x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/hlv-martinez-noi-gi-truoc-tran-anh-vs-bi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Aleksandar Kolarov, c\u1ef1u sao MU \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u1eef d\u1ed9i h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Serbia sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Aleksandar Kolarov b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u1eef d\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay, Serbia c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1edbi Brazil trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018. \u0110\u1ec3 s\u00e1ng c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a\u00a0ch\u00e2u \u00c2u s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Aleksandar Kolarov h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Aleksandar Kolarov h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/aleksandar-kolarov-bi-chi-trich-tham-te-sau-tran-thua-brazil.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Kolarov</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSerbia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng, song h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil. C\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-2. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-brazil-vs-serbia-421-189790.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Braizl vs Serbia</span> khi\u1ebfn Matic v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Aleksandar Kolarov \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, anh m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m trong b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Serbia. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u thi\u1ebfu ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Aleksandar Kolarov, c\u1ef1u sao MU \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u1eef d\u1ed9i h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Serbia sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cKolarov t\u1eebng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t \u1edf Anh, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng theo d\u00f5i c\u1eadu ta thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n cho Man City. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m, nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m trong b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Paulinho, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tha th\u1ee9 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Kolarov tham gia t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 lui v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi 4 b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn t\u1edbi 14 b\u00e0n thua\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Gary Neville \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Serbia</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Serbia \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil, song Gary Neville v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1 cao m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Serbia vs Brazil Casemiro tranh bong\" title=\"Serbia vs Brazil Casemiro tranh bong\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Serbia-vs-Brazil-Casemiro-tranh-bong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Neville v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Serbia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Serbia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t. H\u1ecd t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh Brazil nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i thi\u1ebfu tinh t\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cBrazil r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao h\u01a1n, b\u1edfi v\u1eady vi\u1ec7c Serbia th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfc m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"673","checkdouble":"189824"},{"date":"09:50 28/06","title":"Gi\u00fap SLNA c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi khen c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/giup-slna-co-3-diem-phan-van-duc-nhan-duoc-loi-khen-co-canh-cua-doi-thu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho t\u00e0i n\u0103ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7.</h2><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a SLNA</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 V-League, CLB SLNA \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 4 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp khi ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Vinh. \u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y c\u00e1i duy\u00ean ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i th\u00e0nh.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gi\u00fap SLNA c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi khen h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gi\u00fap SLNA c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi khen h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/7_zing.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng gi\u00fap SLNA h\u1ea1 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Ch\u1ec9 trong 10 ph\u00fat, t\u1eeb ph\u00fat 56 \u0111\u1ebfn 66, </span>tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap SLNA ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-2 chung cu\u1ed9c.</span> \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i t\u1eeb ph\u00eda HLV \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, HLV T\u00e0i Em ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u: \u201cT\u00f4i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, n\u00ean d\u1eb7n c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c k\u1ef9 c\u1eadu ta. Nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ebfc \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01a1i qu\u00e1 hay v\u00e0 l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap. C\u1eadu ta thu\u1ed9c d\u1ea1ng ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1eabn gi\u1eef phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3u thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i h\u1ed3i x\u01b0a\u2019.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 6 n\u00e0y. R\u1ea5t may anh \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng SLNA v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua giai \u0111o\u1ea1n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. L\u00fac n\u00e0y ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i V-League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi 4 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, SLNA l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi b\u1ecf xa nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf v\u1edbi 20 \u0111i\u1ec3m, h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 7 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y, c\u1eeda tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 s\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/27/SLNA-3-2-Sai-Gon.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/slna-vs-sai-gon-vong-16-vleague-2018-372-189729.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/tong-hop-slna-32-sai-gon-vong-16-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/slna-vs-sai-gon-vong-16-vleague-2018-372-189729.html\">SLNA 3-2 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n (KT): Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, CLB x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 4 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc trong 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 H\u1ed3 Ph\u00fac T\u1ecbnh trong hi\u1ec7p 2 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn SLNA c\u00f3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Qua \u0111\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"672","checkdouble":"189826"},{"date":"10:02 28/06","title":"Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 2-2 Costa Rica","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/thong-ke-an-tuong-tran-thuy-sy-22-costa-rica.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 2 l\u1ea7n v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 Costa Rica c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 2-2. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 vs Costa Rica \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t.\r\n</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>3 - </strong>Costa Rica \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n trong 5 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn \u1edf World Cup 2018, nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 vs Costa Rica - B\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 vs Costa Rica - B\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Thong-ke-Thuy-Sy-vs-Costa-Rica---Bang-E-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Costa Rica may m\u1eafn c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 2-2</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>3 - </strong>Yann Sommer l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n th\u1ee9 ba ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 \u1edf m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup, sau Noel Valladares n\u0103m 2014 v\u00e0 Andoni Zubizarreta n\u0103m 1998.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<strong>2 &ndash; </strong><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-thuy-sy-vs-costa-rica-421-189789.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 vs Costa Rica</span> khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ecdi b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf \u0110\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ea3ng E sau Brazil, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u1edf&nbsp;v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<strong>0 &ndash;</strong> L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb World Cup 2006, Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng thua \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<strong>32 &ndash;</strong> Trong s\u1ed1 32 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018, Costa Rica l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng ghi b\u00e0n. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia (0-1) v\u00e0 Brazil (0-2).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<strong>24 &ndash;</strong> B\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Costa Rica \u1edf World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ebfn sau 24 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Costa Rica co duoc 2 ban truoc Thuy Sy\" title=\"Costa Rica c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/095945-costa-rica.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Costa Rica c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<strong>424 &ndash; </strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 vs Costa Rica ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t chu\u1ed7i 424 ph\u00fat kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<strong>6 - </strong>Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf 6/7 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<strong>0 &ndash;</strong> Costa Rica \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0o \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<strong>3 &ndash; </strong>Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u1edf 3 trong 4 l\u1ea7n tham d\u1ef1 World Cup g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y (1994, 2006 v\u00e0 2014), ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 n\u0103m 2010 l\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng&nbsp;b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"671","checkdouble":"189827"},{"date":"10:22 28/06","title":"Aleksandar Kolarov b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch th\u1eadm t\u1ec7 sau tr\u1eadn thua Brazil","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/aleksandar-kolarov-bi-chi-trich-tham-te-sau-tran-thua-brazil.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Aleksandar Kolarov, c\u1ef1u sao MU \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u1eef d\u1ed9i h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Serbia sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Aleksandar Kolarov b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u1eef d\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay, Serbia c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1edbi Brazil trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018. \u0110\u1ec3 s\u00e1ng c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a\u00a0ch\u00e2u \u00c2u s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Aleksandar Kolarov h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Aleksandar Kolarov h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/aleksandar-kolarov-bi-chi-trich-tham-te-sau-tran-thua-brazil.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Kolarov</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSerbia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng, song h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil. C\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-2. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-brazil-vs-serbia-421-189790.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Braizl vs Serbia</span> khi\u1ebfn Matic v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Aleksandar Kolarov \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, anh m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m trong b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Serbia. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u thi\u1ebfu ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Aleksandar Kolarov, c\u1ef1u sao MU \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u1eef d\u1ed9i h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Serbia sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cKolarov t\u1eebng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t \u1edf Anh, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng theo d\u00f5i c\u1eadu ta thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n cho Man City. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m, nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m trong b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Paulinho, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tha th\u1ee9 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Kolarov tham gia t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 lui v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi 4 b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn t\u1edbi 14 b\u00e0n thua\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Gary Neville \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Serbia</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Serbia \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil, song Gary Neville v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1 cao m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Serbia vs Brazil Casemiro tranh bong\" title=\"Serbia vs Brazil Casemiro tranh bong\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Serbia-vs-Brazil-Casemiro-tranh-bong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Neville v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Serbia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Serbia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t. H\u1ecd t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh Brazil nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i thi\u1ebfu tinh t\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cBrazil r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao h\u01a1n, b\u1edfi v\u1eady vi\u1ec7c Serbia th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfc m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"670","checkdouble":"189828"},{"date":"11:18 28/06","title":"Trung v\u1ec7 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/7/20/hlv-conte-khang-dinh-ngung-theo-duoi-koulibaly.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kalidou Koulibaly ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kalidou Koulibaly c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y trung v\u1ec7 Kalidou Koulibaly \u0111\u00e3 duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Napoli, anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 hay nh\u1ea5t Serie A \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"hau ve Koulibaly\" title=\"hau ve Koulibaly\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/10/6/chu-tich-napoli-tiet-lo-gia-khung-chelsea-moi-chao-de-co-koulibaly.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Koulibaly \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 gi\u00fap anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Chelsea, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111ang nh\u1eafm ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Napoli nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Sarri, ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eeba chia tay Napoli \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1eafp d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n The Blues chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i. Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/trung-ve-nay-khien-chelsea-phai-chi-65-trieu-bang-o-he-2018-172-184925.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n ng\u1ecf \u00fd mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Koulibaly</span>, song ph\u00eda Napoli v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKalidou Koulibaly ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu t\u00f4i c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro th\u00ec b\u1ed1 m\u1eb9 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t m\u1eebng. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup 2018, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1o ch\u00ed n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Napoli v\u00e0 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cNhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung thi \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u00f2n chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai do ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i lo li\u1ec7u. N\u1ebfu c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebft k\u1ef9 h\u01a1n h\u00e3y h\u1ecfi \u00f4ng \u1ea5y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kalidou Koulibaly tin Senegal s\u1ebd \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Senegal \u0111ang ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 tr\u1eadn. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi s\u1ebd \u0111i ti\u1ebfp n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Colombia. Kalidou Koulibaly tin Senegal s\u1ebd \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kalidou Koulibaly ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Kalidou Koulibaly ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Kalidou-Koulibaly-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Koulibaly tin Senegal s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. Senegal \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 tu\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1ea3 ch\u00e2u Phi \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng sau Senegal, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Colombia r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"669","checkdouble":"189829"},{"date":"10:13 28/06","title":"\u0110\u00e1 k\u00e9m, ngo\u1ea1i binh c\u1ee7a HAGL s\u1edbm b\u1ecb thanh l\u00fd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/da-kem-ngoai-binh-cua-hagl-som-bi-thanh-ly.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i trong su\u1ed1t giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Rimario Gordon \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3i chia tay CLB HAGL \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 V-League 2018.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>CLB HAGL ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Rimario</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Rimario Gordon l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB HAGL s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y v\u1edbi hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd b\u1ed5 sung s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh cho h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 ph\u1eadp ph\u00f9 c\u1ee7a HAGL. Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng ban \u0111\u1ea7u, ngo\u1ea1i binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Jamaica n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i V-League 2018.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u00e1 k\u00e9m, ngo\u1ea1i binh Rimario s\u1edbm b\u1ecb thanh l\u00fd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u00e1 k\u00e9m, ngo\u1ea1i binh Rimario s\u1edbm b\u1ecb thanh l\u00fd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/thi-dau-kem-hieu-qua-ngoai-binh-cua-hagl-sap-bi-thanh-ly.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ngo\u1ea1i binh Rimario b\u1ecb HAGL ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng sau giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Kh\u00f4ng ghi n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai t\u1ea1i V-League, Rinario c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 n\u00f3ng t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn HAGL quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thanh l\u00fd anh trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Sau v\u00f2ng 16 V-League, BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Rimario. V\u00e0 ngo\u1ea1i binh n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t t\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i th\u00f4ng qua trang facebook c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\"B\u1ea1n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00e0o c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00eam nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y. 6 th\u00e1ng v\u1eeba qua l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c v\u00e0 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao. D\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i chia tay nhau nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ch\u00fac c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i\", Rimario vi\u1ebft. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c lo\u1ea1i Rimario, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 t\u00e1i k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Osmar Francisco. Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Brazil t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u201cG\u1ed7\u201d nh\u01b0ng qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9o d\u00e0i do Osmar d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c 'li h\u00f4n' Rimario th\u00ec CLB HAGL c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Kim Jin-seo, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc cho h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan-168-189697.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan-168-189697.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh: D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n To\u00e0n</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2016, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3 xong m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 \u0111\u00e3 vay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh b\u1eb1ng th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1eadm 4-0 t\u1ea1i Pleiku. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-buc-xuc-voi-trong-tai-bat-tran-hagl-40-than-quang-ninh-168-189698.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-buc-xuc-voi-trong-tai-bat-tran-hagl-40-than-quang-ninh.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-buc-xuc-voi-trong-tai-bat-tran-hagl-40-than-quang-ninh-168-189698.html\">HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng b\u1ee9c x\u00fac v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng thi\u00ean v\u1ecb ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-chia-se-bi-quyet-giup-hoc-tro-danh-bai-than-quang-ninh-168-189699.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/hlv-hagl-chia-se-bi-quyet-giup-hoc-tro-danh-bai-than-quang-ninh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-chia-se-bi-quyet-giup-hoc-tro-danh-bai-than-quang-ninh-168-189699.html\">HLV HAGL chia s\u1ebb b\u00ed quy\u1ebft gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 26/6, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. V\u00e0 HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y?</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-hagl-vs-quang-ninh-325-189652.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/clip-ban-thang-hagl-vs-quang-ninh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-hagl-vs-quang-ninh-325-189652.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: HAGL 4-0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh (V\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018)</span><br>\r\nCLB ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng ngo\u1ea1i binh v\u00e0 to\u00e0n h\u00e0ng c\u00e2y nh\u00e0 l\u00e1 v\u01b0\u1eddn \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng khi ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed,...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"668","checkdouble":"189830"},{"date":"11:32 28/06","title":"Sau v\u00f2ng 16 V-League: HAGL g\u1ecdi, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/sau-vong-16-vleague-hagl-goi-ha-noi-tra-loi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec Vi\u1ec7t Nam hi\u1ec7n nay l\u00e0 HAGL v\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>\u2018G\u1ed7\u2019 \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai</h2>\r\n<h2><o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, HAGL ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 CLB c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 hai tr\u00ean BXH. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cao c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o n\u1ed9i binh, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai s\u1edbm c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau pha b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n \u1edf ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p 1.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sau v\u00f2ng 16 V-League HAGL g\u1ecdi, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sau v\u00f2ng 16 V-League HAGL g\u1ecdi, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HAGL h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 V-League</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ef1 tin, quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i h\u01a1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi sau khi D\u01b0\u01a1ng Thanh H\u00e0o nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf sau pha truy c\u1ea3n V\u0103n To\u00e0n ghi b\u00e0n, HAGL ghi th\u00eam 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u1eefa do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 4-0 chung cu\u1ed9c. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eadm nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a HAGL \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ed1p \u0111\u1ea7u, \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c tinh th\u1ea7n to l\u1edbn gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/26/HAGL-4-0-Quang-Ninh.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 V-League, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby, ph\u00e1o \u0111\u00e0i b\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 x\u00e2m ph\u1ea1m \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. G\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u0111ang sa s\u00fat, kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 ch\u01a1i l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd t\u1edbi ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Samson m\u1edbi l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 13 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. V\u1edbi th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i n\u00e0y, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gia t\u0103ng kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng. Sau v\u00f2ng 16, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf xa \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp sau t\u1edbi 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y d\u00f9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n 10 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ha Noi vs Quang Nam\" title=\"H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/ha-noi-vs-quang-nam-vong-16-vleague-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i to\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam t\u1ea1i V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Thanh H\u00f3a th\u0103ng hoa<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn thua H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng 0-2 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 12 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec9nh \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a. Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng \u00edt ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 lo l\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng g\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1eady n\u1ed5i. Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 thay \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00f3 tin \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u 13 sau khi h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Thanh \u0111\u00e3 \u2018h\u1ed3i sinh\u2019 v\u1edbi m\u1ea1ch tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, r\u1ed3i XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 v\u00e0 Becamex B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng. V\u00e0 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 4 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. Ghi 7 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n, v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 hai tr\u00ean BXH, \u0111\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 ngo\u00e0i mong \u0111\u1ee3i v\u1edbi FLC Thanh H\u00f3a. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u tho\u00e1t b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Thanh H\u00f3a hay SLNA, CLB b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh c\u0169ng \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00e1ng kinh ng\u1ea1c trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1. L\u00fac n\u00e0y Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111ang c\u00f3 tinh th\u1ea7n r\u1ea5t cao, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB TP.HCM \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 15. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec v\u1eady, tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t hi v\u1ecdng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV V\u0103n S\u1ef9 s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 theo c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1ecdt ng\u00e0o h\u01a1n khi ghi t\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong chu\u1ed7i 4 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ec1u gi\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m, trong \u0111\u00f3 3 tr\u1eadn gi\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i, CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 12, t\u1ea1o kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch 2 v\u00e0 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 TP.HCM v\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n. \u0110\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam d\u00f9 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u1ecd t\u1eebng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd nh\u1ea5t cho su\u1ea5t xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00f2ng 16, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111ang x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng 12/14 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i. \u1ede v\u00f2ng ti\u1ebfp theo, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u S\u00e0i G\u00f2n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t, n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u2018chung k\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1ee3c\u2019 n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u0129 trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH V-League 2018 sau vong 16\" title=\"BXH V-League 2018 sau v\u00f2ng 16\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Untitled.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>BXH V-League 2018 sau v\u00f2ng 16</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-chia-se-bi-quyet-giup-hoc-tro-danh-bai-than-quang-ninh-168-189699.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/hlv-hagl-chia-se-bi-quyet-giup-hoc-tro-danh-bai-than-quang-ninh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-chia-se-bi-quyet-giup-hoc-tro-danh-bai-than-quang-ninh-168-189699.html\">HLV HAGL chia s\u1ebb b\u00ed quy\u1ebft gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 26/6, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. V\u00e0 HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y?</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-buc-xuc-voi-trong-tai-bat-tran-hagl-40-than-quang-ninh-168-189698.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-buc-xuc-voi-trong-tai-bat-tran-hagl-40-than-quang-ninh.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-buc-xuc-voi-trong-tai-bat-tran-hagl-40-than-quang-ninh-168-189698.html\">HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng b\u1ee9c x\u00fac v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng thi\u00ean v\u1ecb ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan-168-189697.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan-168-189697.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh: D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n To\u00e0n</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2016, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3 xong m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 \u0111\u00e3 vay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh b\u1eb1ng th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1eadm 4-0 t\u1ea1i Pleiku. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"667","checkdouble":"189833"},{"date":"11:58 28/06","title":"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 ng\u00e0y 28/6: Kroos nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 sau d\u00f2ng tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i nh\u1ee5c m\u1ea1 Brazil","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/28/ngay-hom-nay-286.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (28/6). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi b\u00e1m s\u00e1t t\u1eebng chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh.</h2>(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)<br>\r\n<h2>Toni Kroos nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 sau d\u00f2ng tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i nh\u1ee5c m\u1ea1 Brazil</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">C\u0110V Brazil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 t\u1ed5ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Kroos v\u00ec c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u0103ng b\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh m\u1ec9a mai tr\u1eadn thua 1-7 c\u1ee7a Selecao tr\u01b0\u1edbc \"C\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng\" \u1edf World Cup 2014.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/anh15.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n31/12/2016, Toni Kroos khi\u1ebfn C\u0110V Brazil n\u00f3ng m\u1eaft khi \u0111\u0103ng b\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh ch\u00fac m\u1eebng n\u0103m m\u1edbi 2017 \u0111\u1ea7y \u1ea9n \u00fd. L\u00e1 c\u1edd Brazil v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ea1nh nhau t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0ng cho th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-7 c\u1ee7a Selecao tr\u01b0\u1edbc Die Mannschaft t\u1ea1i World Cup 2014. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 k\u00fd \u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Samba n\u00e0o mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eafc l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u01a1n 1 n\u0103m sau, C\u0110V Brazil m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \"tr\u1ea3 th\u00f9\" Toni Kroos. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi\u00a0 \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1eddi th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p \"ch\u00fac m\u1eebng n\u0103m 2018\" v\u1edbi h\u00e0m \u00fd ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-2 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018. L\u00e1 c\u1edd H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ea1nh \u0110\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0ng cho t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0 sau g\u1ea7n 100 ph\u00fat b\u00f3ng l\u0103n tr\u00ean SV\u0110 Kazan.</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110T Brazil tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft cho ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng E</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Ni\u1ec1m vui chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Brazil tr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n khi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i Marcelo g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1eaft l\u01b0ng. Ni\u1ec1m vui chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Brazil tr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n khi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i Marcelo g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1eaft l\u01b0ng. Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, L\u0110B\u0110 Brazil (CBF) x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng, Mercelo b\u1ecb co th\u1eaft c\u01a1 l\u01b0ng. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, c\u01a1 quan quy\u1ec1n l\u1ef1c nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Samba c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u1ea5n an ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 30 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/brazil-nhan-tin-du-sau-khi-danh-bai-serbia-469-189804.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/brazil-nhan-tin-du-sau-khi-danh-bai-serbia.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/brazil-nhan-tin-du-sau-khi-danh-bai-serbia-469-189804.html\">Brazil nh\u1eadn tin d\u1eef sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Serbia</span><br>\r\n<span>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Marcelo \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb r\u00fat ra kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n s\u1edbm trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Brazil v\u00e0 Serbia \u0111\u00eam qua v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Kaka m\u00e1ch n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Brazil gi\u00fap Neymar t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng</h2>\r\n<div>C\u1ef1u sao Brazil, Kaka \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Brazil c\u1ea7n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 Neymar \u0111\u1ec3 anh s\u1edbm l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. \"Neymar c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian. Ch\u00fang ta v\u1eabn nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y qua t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 cho \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Neymar v\u00e0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i ng\u00e0y c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u01a1i phong \u0111\u1ed9. N\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i 100% th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng, Brazil ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 s\u00e1u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi\".</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/kaka-mach-nuoc-de-dt-brazil-bien-neymar-toa-sang-tai-world-cup-421-189811.html\">Kaka m\u00e1ch n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Brazil gi\u00fap Neymar t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>FIFA d\u1ecda tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t Maradona</h2>\r\n<div>Nh\u1eefng h\u00e0nh vi c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch hay th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 th\u00f4 l\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Diego Maradona trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Argentina \u2013 Nigeria \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D World Cup c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina n\u00e0y b\u1ecb FIFA b\u00e3i b\u1ecf ch\u1ee9c v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ea1i s\u1ee9 thi\u1ec7n ch\u00ed c\u1ee7a t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c n\u00e0y. Maradona \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3 t\u1edbi 110.000 b\u1ea3ng + \u0111\u00e0i th\u1ecd chi ph\u00ed \u0103n \u1edf cho m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n tham d\u1ef1 c\u00e1c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n do FIFA y\u00eau c\u1ea7u, nh\u01b0ng FIFA gi\u1edd \u0111ang gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t h\u00e0nh vi c\u1ee7a Maradona n\u1ebfu \u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u00f3 c\u1eed ch\u1ec9 ch\u0129a \u201cng\u00f3n tay th\u1ed1i\u201d nh\u01b0 v\u1eeba qua.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay, tin t\u1ee9c World Cup ng\u00e0y 286 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay, tin t\u1ee9c World Cup ng\u00e0y 286 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Tin-nong-World-Cup-2018-hom-nay,-tin-tuc-World-Cup-ngay-286-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Diego Maradona</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Ospina tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Colombia</h2>\r\n<div>Colombia s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn g\u1eb7p Senegal \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out \u1edf b\u1ea3ng H, v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00f3n tin vui khi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n David Ospina s\u1ebd k\u1ecbp ra s\u00e2n sau khi b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eb9. Colombia s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Abel Aguilar do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng vai, nh\u01b0ng Aguilar d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i ra s\u00e2n n\u1ebfu Colombia v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<h2>Eriksen th\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Modric</h2>\r\n<div>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0110an M\u1ea1ch s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Croatia \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Christian Eriksen c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch cho bi\u1ebft anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Luka Modric. \u201cLuka r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng. \u0110\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t b\u1edfi kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Luka m\u00e0 c\u00f2n v\u00ec anh \u1ea5y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Tottenham tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y\u201d, Eriksen n\u00f3i.</div>\r\n<h2>Ch\u00e2u Phi c\u00f3 k\u1ef3 World Cup t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t trong 36 n\u0103m</h2>\r\n<div>V\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n Senegal l\u00e0 c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp trong s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u00e2u Phi. Ai C\u1eadp, Morocco, Nigeria v\u00e0 Tunisia \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu Senegal thua Colombia c\u00f2n Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng thua Ba Lan th\u00ec v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1ebd s\u1ea1ch b\u00f3ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u Phi. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb World Cup 1986 v\u00f2ng knock-out lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u00e2u Phi ngay c\u1ea3 khi ch\u00e2u Phi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 su\u1ea5t.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"666","checkdouble":"189835"},{"date":"08:34 28/06","title":"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec trong ng\u00e0y Brazil nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng h\u1ea1 Serbia 2-0?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/thay-gi-trong-ngay-brazil-nhe-nhang-ha-serbia-20.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Brazil vs Serbia kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ee7ng \u0111\u1ec9nh nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea7y hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Samba. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i chi ti\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd kh\u00e1c trong m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Otkrytiye Arena.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Serbia 0-2 Brazil\r\n<div style=\"text - align:center; width: 100 %; padding: 20px 0; \"><video class=\"hlsvideoobj\" data-src=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/DRM/HLS/201806/274130/master.m3u8\" controls=\"\"></video></div>\r\n</em></div>\r\n<h2>Brazil nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBrazil b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Serbia b\u1eb1ng t\u00e2m th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t thi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1. M\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 Selecao ghi t\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 n\u00f4n n\u00f3ng t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Brazil gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Serbia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Tite \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 ra m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u01b0u ti\u00ean s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ee7a Brazil \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Trong th\u1ebf bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i d\u00e2ng cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, Serbia \u0111\u00e3 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1eaby m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Samba gi\u0103ng ra. Ph\u00fat 36, t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i si\u00eau h\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a Philippe Coutinho, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a anh t\u1ea1i Barcelona l\u00e0 Paulinho c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Stojkovic v\u00e0 nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec trong ng\u00e0y Brazil nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng h\u1ea1 Serbia 2-0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec trong ng\u00e0y Brazil nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng h\u1ea1 Serbia 2-0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Brazil-nhe-nhang-vuot-qua-Serbia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Brazil kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Serbia 2-0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, Brazil c\u00e0ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Serbia kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed khoa h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Brazil c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u00eam 1 b\u00e0n n\u1eefa do c\u00f4ng Thiago Silva xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Neymar.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong ng\u00e0y \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 s\u1edbm b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, Brazil l\u1ea1i nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng E. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 VCK World Cup th\u1ee9 13 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong 12 l\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Brazil 3 l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch (1970, 1994 v\u00e0 2002), 1 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft (1998), 1 l\u1ea7n \u0111o\u1ea1t gi\u1ea3i 3 (1978) v\u00e0 2 l\u1ea7n c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch th\u1ee9 4 (1974 v\u00e0 2014). V\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f9ng phong c\u00e1ch h\u1ee3p th\u1eddi, Selecao h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd c\u00f2n \u1edf l\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga cho t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng Marcelo, kh\u00f4ng sao</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Marcelo d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 r\u1eddi s\u00e2n ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 10 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V Brazil lo l\u1eafng. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y s\u1ea3y ch\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia, \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Brazil vs Serbia s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi t\u00ean c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng Real Madrid v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League 3 m\u00f9a li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec trong ng\u00e0y Brazil nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng h\u1ea1 Serbia 2-0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec trong ng\u00e0y Brazil nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng h\u1ea1 Serbia 2-0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Thay-gi-trong-ngay-Brazil-nhe-nhang-ha-Serbia-2-0-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">S\u1ef1 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Marcelo kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn Selecao qu\u00e1 lo ng\u1ea1i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, Marcelo v\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t, nh\u01b0ng theo chi\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng l\u1ea1c quan h\u01a1n cho Brazil. S\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf mang t\u00ean Filipe Luis h\u1eb3n v\u1eabn khi\u1ebfn HLV Tite h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. C\u00f3 Marcelo tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, Brazil s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cung c\u1ea5p th\u00eam nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng song \u0111\u00f4i l\u00fac phong c\u00e1ch d\u00e2ng cao c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t y\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 khai th\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi Brazil, b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ngh\u1ec7 s\u0129 nh\u01b0 Neymar v\u00e0 Coutinho hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n. Nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Filipe \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia, anh r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p trong vai tr\u00f2 b\u1ecdc l\u00f3t cho hai ng\u00f4i sao tr\u00ean. V\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Atletico Madrid \u1edf ph\u00eda sau, Neymar v\u00e0 Coutinho c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng l\u1edbn m\u00e0 Marcelo hay \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i ph\u00eda sau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-serbia-461-189793.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-serbia.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-serbia-461-189793.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Serbia 0-2 Brazil (B\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\n<span>Kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, Selecao ch\u1eb3ng g\u1eb7p qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Serbia. H\u1ecd \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i v\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01b0a r\u00f5 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Marcelo, nh\u01b0ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ebft \u0111au th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00edch c\u1ee7a Filipe, Brazil kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i qu\u00e1 \u00e2u lo v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 Serbia c\u00f2n h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u1eb7t Serbia v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t. Th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf ph\u00fat 36 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh &ldquo;\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng&rdquo; c\u00e0ng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. Khi \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c C\u0110V ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i s\u1ef1 qu\u1eadt kh\u1edfi t\u1eeb Serbia \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien dao Mitrovic tiec nuoi\" title=\"tien dao Mitrovic tiec nuoi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/tien-dao-Mitrovic-tiec-nuoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Serbia d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n ngay sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra. \u0110\u1ebfn 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, Serbia c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 hu\u1ed1ng chi l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd t\u1edbi sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng Alek Mitrovic. Trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t Fagner 1m68, \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eadt l\u00ean r\u1ea5t cao nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng tr\u00fang v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u00f3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Serbia ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil. Gi\u1ea3 s\u1eed Selecao mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n thay v\u00ec \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng hay ch\u00ed \u00edt l\u00e0 ch\u1eaft chiu c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i h\u01a1n, s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thu\u1ed9c Nam T\u01b0 c\u0169 s\u1ebd c\u00f2n gia t\u0103ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-brazil-vs-serbia-463-189782.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-serbia.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-brazil-vs-serbia-463-189782.html\">Serbia 0-2 Brazil (KT): D\u1ea1o ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Moscow, Selecao k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1</span><br>\r\n<span>Kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, Selecao ch\u1eb3ng g\u1eb7p qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Serbia. H\u1ecd \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i v\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSerbia v\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ec3 ra Milinkovic-Savic, Nemanja Matic hay Alek Kolarov. Nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00e1nh v\u00e1c n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 Serbia t\u1ea7m th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch &ldquo;Ng\u1ef1a \u00f4&rdquo; \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c giao tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 s\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>C\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Brazil</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ed7i khi Brazil thi \u0111\u1ea5u, m\u1ecdi \u00e1nh m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ed3n v\u00e0o Neymar. Ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 x\u1ee9 Samba l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i m\u1edbi b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u00e0n ch\u00e2n kh\u00e1 n\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 1 th\u00e1ng. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi n\u1ed7i lo t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c l\u00fac ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Neymar \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ed1i \u01b0u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Serbia vs Brazil Coutinho di bong\" title=\"Serbia vs Brazil Coutinho di bong\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Serbia-vs-Brazil-Coutinho-di-bong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Coutinho l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Brazil vs Serbia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ed7i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00f4i qua, Neymar l\u1ea1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. \u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, &ldquo;Ti\u1ec3u Pele&rdquo; im ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e1 r\u1eafn \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n anh. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica, Neymar \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa s\u1ee9c \u00e9p v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 cho Brazil. V\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia, Neymar ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n v\u1edbi qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ec3 Thiago Silva ghi b\u00e0n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Brazil vs Serbia s\u1ebd l\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu s\u00f3t n\u1ebfu b\u1ecf qua Coutinho. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n t\u1eeb ni\u00ean thi\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a Neymar g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y trong c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Selecao. Sau 1 b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y S\u0129, 1 b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Barcelona l\u1ea1i tung \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n tuy\u1ec7t h\u1ea3o gi\u00fap Paulinho khai th\u00f4ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc tr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-brazil-noi-gi-sau-chien-thang-truoc-serbia-421-189815.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/ngoi-sao-thu-5-va-nhung-giac-mo-con-dang-do.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-brazil-noi-gi-sau-chien-thang-truoc-serbia-421-189815.html\">HLV Brazil n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia?</span><br>\r\nHLV Tite ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs Serbia, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 57 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Selecao c\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i c\u00e0ng hay \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1edbi gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 6 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, Brazil s\u1ebd d\u1ef1a nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o Neymar v\u00e0 Coutinho. \u0110\u1ebfn gi\u1edd, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Serbia 0-2 Brazil\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Serbia 0-2 Brazil\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Thong-so-Brazil.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Serbia 0-2 Brazil</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 2-0 Serbia tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-brazil-20-serbia-421-189806.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 2-0 Serbia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/brazil-nhan-tin-du-sau-khi-danh-bai-serbia-469-189804.html\">Brazil nh\u1eadn tin d\u1eef sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Serbia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-serbia-khang-dinh-choi-tren-chan-brazil-465-189798.html\">HLV Mladen Krstajic: Serbia ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean ch\u00e2n Brazil trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-serbia-461-189793.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Serbia 0-2 Brazil (B\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-brazil-vs-serbia-421-189790.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Serbia vs Brazil tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-brazil-vs-serbia-463-189782.html\">Serbia 0-2 Brazil (KT): D\u1ea1o ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Moscow, Selecao k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"665","checkdouble":"189803"},{"date":"07:37 28/06","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (28/6/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-2862018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='c